\begin_inset Formula $\left[0,1\right]\backslash C_{n}$
\end_inset

 e tale che 
\begin_inset Formula $f_{n}(0)=0$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f_{n}(1)=1$
\end_inset

.
