\begin_inset Formula $k=1,2,\dots$
\end_inset

, scegliamo 
\begin_inset Formula $n_{k}$
\end_inset

 tale che 
\begin_inset Formula $n_{k+1}\geq n_{k}$
\end_inset

 e:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\intop_{X}\left|f_{n_{k}}-f\right|\text{d}\mu<2^{-k}.
\]

\end_inset

Posto 
\begin_inset Formula $h=\sum_{k=1}^{\infty}\left|f_{n_{k}}-f\right|$
