\[
\mathscr{C}(E)=\left\{ F\subseteq X\vert E\backslash F,F\backslash E,E\cap F\in\mathscr{C}(\mathscr{A})\right\} .
\]

\end_inset

Si vede facilmente che 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathscr{C}(E)$
\end_inset

