\begin_inset Formula $F\in\mathscr{C}(E)$
\end_inset

 per ogni 
\begin_inset Formula $F\in\mathscr{A}$
\end_inset

.
 Quindi 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathscr{A}\subseteq\mathscr{C}(E)$
\end_inset

, da cui 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathscr{C}(\mathscr{A})\subseteq\mathscr{C}(E)$
\end_inset

