\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathscr{A}_{n}=\left\{ x\in\mathbb{R}\vert\lambda_{F}(\left\{ x\right\} )>\frac{1}{n}\right\} 
\]

\end_inset

e, poichè:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lambda_{F}^{*}(\mathscr{A}_{n})\leq\lambda_{F}(\left[a,b\right])=F(b)-F(a-)=F(b)-F(a)<\infty
\]

\end_inset

si ha che ogni 
