\begin_inset Formula $h_{n}\in C_{c}(X)$
\end_inset

 tali che 
\begin_inset Formula $0\leq h_{n}\leq1$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $h_{n}(x)=1$
\end_inset

 per ogni 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in K_{n}$
\end_inset

