\begin_inset Formula $g\in C_{c}(X)$
\end_inset

 tale che:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mu(\left\{ \chi_{K}f(x)\neq g(x)\right\} )<\frac{\varepsilon}{2}.
\]

\end_inset

