\begin_inset Formula $S_{1}'=S_{1}\cap F\supseteq E\cap F$
\end_inset

 e 
\begin_inset Formula $S_{2}'=S_{2}\backslash F\supseteq E\backslash F$
\end_inset

.
 Inoltre 
\begin_inset Formula $S_{1}'$
